  "description": "How to customize the DocumentToolbar component \u2014 container classes, button child selectors, and revision history scoping",
  "orientation": "The DocumentToolbar exposes three independent styling layers. The container accepts className with twMerge for conflict resolution. Internal buttons have no dedicated props and require Tailwind arbitrary child selectors. Revision history renders outside the editor tree, requiring scoped CSS. This topic is part of the Editors and UX domain.",
